### Step 1: Analyze PR
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/analyze-pr
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "repo_url": "{{repo_url}}",
  "pr_number": {{pr_number}},
  "github_token": "{{github_token}}"
}

### Step 2: Check Task Status
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/status/{{task_id}}
Accept: application/json

### Step 3: Get Result
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/result/{{task_id}}
Accept: application/json
